disclaimer: work in progress

dependencies:
=============
* openfst-1.3.2
* libLBFGS
* python 2.7

how to build (compiler: gcc 4.6.3 or clang 3.1-8):
==================================================
* make

how to run:
===========
* example invocations can be found at batch-files/run-small-example.bash, which uses a small parallel corpus of english-kinyarwanda located in the 'example' subdirectory
